                            <resolved>Wed, 19 Aug 2015 19:19:49 +0000</resolved>
                                        <fixVersion>3.0 beta 1</fixVersion>
                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>2</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14702250" author="bdeggleston" created="Wed, 19 Aug 2015 00:57:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is a driver issue. The index row logic is attempting to associate all indexes from a given keyspace with all tables in that keyspace.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve created a ticket and submitted a pull request here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://datastax-oss.atlassian.net/browse/JAVA-882&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://datastax-oss.atlassian.net/browse/JAVA-882&lt;/a&gt;, and will submit a patch once that gets merged. This fixes the deterministic breakage for CqlTableTest, although there&apos;s still some sporadic failures caused by other issues (OOM, etc).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14702262" author="iamaleksey" created="Wed, 19 Aug 2015 01:11:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you. Those sporadic issues are not new, and out of scope of this issue, so don&apos;t worry about them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=beobal&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;beobal&quot;&gt;beobal&lt;/a&gt; to review&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14703511" author="bdeggleston" created="Wed, 19 Aug 2015 18:21:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;here&apos;s the patch with the updated driver: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/bdeggleston/cassandra/tree/10121-2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/bdeggleston/cassandra/tree/10121-2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14703603" author="iamaleksey" created="Wed, 19 Aug 2015 19:19:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks. Built a jar from java-driver &lt;tt&gt;java875&lt;/tt&gt; branch and committed to cassandra-3.0 as &lt;tt&gt;51bc7f87d708abb66db73976e5a60df8e53c7c4a&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
